{"word":"ἐξευρετέος","slug":"ἐξευρετέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξευρετέος</b></el> <el>(ἐξευρετέος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐξευρίσκω'><el>ἐξευρίσκω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be discovered</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>ἐξευρετέον</el>, <i>one must find out</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}